{"type": "article", "id": 54, "title": "安迪·沃霍尔又有12张“新作”问世", "description": "安迪·沃霍尔又有12张“新作”问世", "date": "2014-04-28T20:45:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 7, "name": "艺术"}, {"id": 166, "name": "安迪·沃霍尔"}, {"id": 167, "name": "卡耐基梅隆大学"}, {"id": 168, "name": "Cory Arcangel"}], "category": 18, "author": 2, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 1, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606152748TvW26LY10CheQmqa.jpg", "contents": "\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">\r\n\t1985年的阿米加电脑的硬盘里发现了<a href=\"http://www.huhmagazine.co.uk/6705/12-unknown-warhol-works-recovered-from-amiga-computer-disks\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">安迪·沃霍尔12幅从未曝光过的作品</a>。安迪·沃霍尔的粉丝兼艺术家Cory Arcangel于2011年在安迪·沃霍尔博物馆档案里发现了这些磁盘，卡耐基梅隆大学的电脑实验室又花了3年时间，总算把这些图像从一堆模糊的数据中恢复出来。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t题图来自<a href=\"http://www.huhmagazine.co.uk/6705/12-unknown-warhol-works-recovered-from-amiga-computer-disks\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">huhmagazine</a> \r\n</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n"}